    "text": "🇺🇸 ELON EYES 2028: MIGHT BACK VANCE INSTEAD OF THIRD PARTY\n\nInstead of splitting the GOP vote with his America Party, he's reportedly considering throwing his war chest behind JD Vance for 2028.\n\nVP Vance: \n\n\"My hope is that by the time of the midterms, he's kind of come back into the fold\"\n\nSource: Wall Street Journal",
